{"id": "769c5c9837ea81081c4c415c701e4189b5f9a97bbb2be00351669c81af4de834", "item_id": "52376761a8:0", "text": "In Katana there are 2 ways to setup Stylized Looks:"}
{"id": "7de34b0855c1917adc00e6b50d8d8b93a5c64c8d5a7c2a7e43906808bdc08a73", "item_id": "52376761a8:1", "text": "A simple \"beginner\" Macro that has everything in it."}
{"id": "661b8fc7ddebb4e0b2f73d0dea43c3b58c733a5e04cc40b024c16b0d9aebc39d", "item_id": "52376761a8:2", "text": "A more advanced manual option for the user to set everything up manually, with more control and daisy-chain options."}
{"id": "a2ddfe7a5f62d4d6f28c911e4ae5b97438e7148608ab5d346ff71fdfd3a519c7", "item_id": "52376761a8:3", "text": "The beginner macro looks like this:"}
{"id": "630f2b06ff1a96709b36ef5f6723df79d3a69e19063c13bf8e660d9017f3fb3b", "item_id": "52376761a8:4", "text": "In the macro, there are 3 nodes: Toon, Hatching, and Lines."}
{"id": "96e744a5da217a13492320fb297e621e2a58a829ff68d6eb01968bc5c239b9e4", "item_id": "52376761a8:5", "text": "Outside the macro, there is also the StylizedControl node, which is connected to PxrSurface like this:"}
{"id": "2f21efeab59014149e6093c8e523f0d4aff24d29725c9888d55e2ca9b00d1953", "item_id": "52376761a8:6", "text": "If the Stylized Looks macro isn't already in your scene, simply add it from scratch by hitting Tab in the Nodegraph, and it will appear in the menu like this:"}
{"id": "a6c42b5791a75172e1a482d500f5dc5197b959b6855b9ebaec22eb6461b9ce18", "item_id": "52376761a8:7", "text": "Then, we add a shading node from the same menu:"}
{"id": "95add7f66b1af2408280416740942006bce281b5f744baf8cd18882f120cba55", "item_id": "52376761a8:8", "text": "Then select"}
{"id": "d283ef081c33967f2c80c57228ce9f4d2e9836ee4afbe1e7303455a199d48d35", "item_id": "52376761a8:9", "text": "PxrStylizedControl"}
{"id": "7040f6258157531dbcb8698eba76f6b366af2d39b3cab1b1102e8b19f8f811e0", "item_id": "52376761a8:11", "text": "and connect"}
{"id": "e768f64d396a382d8043d4888c8b7c15e35dd3007d6f1b5907183ddff6b53670", "item_id": "52376761a8:12", "text": "resultAOV"}
{"id": "663ea1bfffe5038f3f0cf667f14c4257eff52d77ce7f2a218f72e9286616ea39", "item_id": "52376761a8:13", "text": "to"}
{"id": "3eeb4e6700fd6bb7868c41ba22d0428ebbc7281ba15d4b587240937c1cbc1e4b", "item_id": "52376761a8:14", "text": "utilityPattern"}
{"id": "b8d31e852725afb1e26d53bab6095b2bff1749c9275be13ed1c05a56ed31ec09", "item_id": "52376761a8:15", "text": "on"}
